name: Buildings Screen print
description:
Hand screen printed black buildings illustration on white 220gsm paper.

- Signed and numbered limited edition to 35 
- Print measures 42 x 29.7cm (A3) to fit standard frames
- Ships rolled in stiff postal tube
- Illustrated and printed by Alex Foster at Resort Studios
- Free postage

name: Illustrated Card model kits
description:
A pack of illustrated 3d animal models for you to cut out, assemble and use as decoration or to play with.

- Signed and numbered edition of 100
- Pack includes Stag, Bear and Dinosaur model kits
- Double sided print on quality 350gsm card
- Doubles as free standing decoration
- Free UK postage

Illustration by Alex Foster

name: Illustrated tree decorations
description:
An illustrated family of reindeer for you to cut out, assemble and hang on your tree.

- Signed and numbered edition of 100
- Mum, Dad and child reindeer
- Double sided print on quality 350gsm card
- Doubles as free standing decoration
- Free UK postage

Illustration by Alex Foster

name: Snowman Christmas Card pack
description:
Wish your friends and family a Happy Christmas with these illustrated Christmas cards

- Signed and numbered edition of 100
- Pack of 5 A6 cards
- Printed on quality 300gsm card
- Blank inside
- Free UK postage

Illustration by Alex Foster
